Title: Diving Normal
Writer: Scotty Crowe (story), Ashlin Halfnight, Philipp Karner (story)
Actors: Susie Abromeit, Philipp Karner, Scotty Crowe, Sandra Bernhard
Plot: Fulton, an ambitious Brooklynite graphic novelist, and Gordon, his socially awkward neighbor, are best friends who both vie for the attention of Dana, a beautiful but damaged girl.
